  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb7\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u2013\u00a0 \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Soon the Rajapaksas will come to power \u2013 Sagara Kariyavasam",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "We have done political maneuvering to weaken the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government rather than the opposition paying attention.",
        "The Rajapaksas will regain power. Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna General Secretary Sagara Kariyawasam said that we will definitely improve the national economy.",
        "Speaking at a press conference held at the office of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna on Thursday (28), he stated the above.",
        "Amidst great expectations of the people of the country, former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa formed a government with a two-thirds majority.",
        "The global impact of the Covid pandemic has affected Sri Lanka for the past two years.",
        "In the midst of the Covid impact, the dilemma of whether to protect the economy or protect the people has emerged.",
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa mentioned in the cabinet that priority should be given to protecting the people of the country from the impact of Covid and that we will face the economic impact with one accord.",
        "The plan to protect the country from the impact of covid-19 was a success but the economic crisis intensified. A few members of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna turned the economic crisis into a political crisis.",
        "The people of the country now understand that we have been close by and weakened the government by political maneuvering rather than the opposition paying attention to weaken the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramun-led government.",
        "The Rajapaksas will regain power very soon. We will definitely improve the national economy. He said that our main goal is to implement the policy plan for a prosperous future."
      ],
